text: Bishkurayevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Bishkurayevsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 433 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Verkhneyarkeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District
title: Bishkurayevo
